<section id="servicesContainer" class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default service">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h4>Social Media Strategy <span class="fa fa-globe"></span></h4>
                    <p>Looking to <strong>grow your brands online presence</strong>? Social media is an important key to creating and maintaining a successful business. It’s our goal to optimize content for your social media platforms (i.e. Twitter, Facebook, Pinterest, Linked In, Google +, Instagram) through strategic methods that work for your brand.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default service">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h4>Content Creation <span class="fa fa-rss"></span></h4>
                    <p>The quality of the content on your site is important and lets your readers know who you are. We'll help you <strong>create engaging and visible content</strong> (ie. blog posts, graphics, advertisements, etc..) to help attract readers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default service">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h4>Media Outreach <span class="fa fa-comments"></span></h4>
                    <p>Have a great product or service you’re currently trying to promote? We’ll get you in touch with some of the internet's top influencers and trendsetters and help <strong>build buzz and engagement</strong> for you and your business.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default service">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h4>Marketing Consulting <span class="fa fa-desktop"></span></h4>
                    <p>Creating and building your brand requires a lot of time and effort. It’s our goal to help jumpstart your business and/or blog by teaching you the key fundamentals, discussing strategic methods, as well as answering any questions you may have.</p>
                    <p>(Popular topics are: Social Media Tips/Tricks, Sponsored Collaborations, How to Turn your Blog into a Business, How to Build a Following, Increasing Readership, How to Get Your Readers Engaged, Building an Online Presence)
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row servicePitch">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <h5>Interested in any of our services?</h5>
            <!-- <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1uTBZqoY5HjB4N2MQNdZlbz2pW0zRmKUxG8SIp_9BqyM/viewform" class="btn btn-primary ft-link-btn">Submit an Inquiry</a> -->
            <a id="go" href="#inquiryModal" name="inquiryModal" rel="leanModal" class="btn btn-primary ft-link-btn">Submit an Inquiry</a>
            <em>I can't wait to hear from you!</em>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-6" id="inquiryModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
    <div class="lean-modal-header">
        <a id="lean-modal-close" href="#" class="pull-right"><i class="fa fa-times-circle"></i></a>
    </div>
    <%= form_tag('inquiry', remote: true, class: 'form') do %>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="contact-email">Your e-mail: </label>
        <input id="contact-email" name="email" type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="your@email.com" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="contact-name">Name: </label>
        <input id="contact-name" name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="name" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="contact-name">Website: </label>
        <input id="contact-name" name="name" type="url" class="form-control" placeholder="website" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="contact-message">What services are you interested in?</label>
        <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-default">Send</button>
    <% end %>
</div>